      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلْحِجَامَةِ وَ حَلْقِ اَلْقَفَا فِي أَشْهُرِ اَلْحَجِّ قَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ وَ لاَ بَأْسَ بِالنُّورَةِ وَ اَلسِّوَاكِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2521 - It is narrated from Sama‘ah, who said:\nI asked Imam (as) about cupping and shaving the nape during the months of Hajj.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it, nor in using Nuura (depilatory cream) or a toothstick (siwak).\""
        ]
      }
